1
00:00:03,937 --> 00:00:05,572
I'll go get you some honey water.

2
00:00:06,539 --> 00:00:08,274
Just stay here and wait for me.

3
00:00:16,549 --> 00:00:18,451
I actually came back for you then.

4
00:00:19,586 --> 00:00:20,586
But...

5
00:00:20,987 --> 00:00:23,256
I saw you getting cozy with someone else.

6
00:00:24,424 --> 00:00:26,393
I thought you'd moved on.

7
00:00:27,994 --> 00:00:28,994
Wait, what?

8
00:00:29,429 --> 00:00:30,964
You said you loved me.

9
00:00:31,631 --> 00:00:33,433
I was only gone for a few months.

10
00:00:34,234 --> 00:00:35,834
How could you start dating someone else?

11
00:00:36,736 --> 00:00:37,837
I wasn't dating anyone.

12
00:00:38,505 --> 00:00:39,639
Yes, you were!

13
00:00:44,110 --> 00:00:45,245
Excuse me?

14
00:00:45,645 --> 00:00:47,012
That wasn't a "breakup."

15
00:00:47,013 --> 00:00:48,381
I was dumped.

16
00:00:49,270 --> 00:00:50,258
I wasn't in the right headspace

17
00:00:50,283 --> 00:00:51,951
to jump into a new relationship.

18
00:00:52,752 --> 00:00:54,320
You must have seen someone else.

19
00:00:55,422 --> 00:00:56,422
So...

20
00:00:57,323 --> 00:00:58,591
I wasn't seeing anyone then,

21
00:01:00,326 --> 00:01:01,494
and I'm not

22
00:01:02,462 --> 00:01:03,763
seeing anyone now.

23
00:01:08,168 --> 00:01:10,103
If that's the case...

24
00:01:17,644 --> 00:01:18,978
What are you saying?

25
00:01:26,152 --> 00:01:27,587
I, Chen Xiaoan,

26
00:01:28,421 --> 00:01:30,490
am truly sorry for the mistake

27
00:01:31,124 --> 00:01:32,525
I made back then.

28
00:01:33,226 --> 00:01:34,226
I've decided

29
00:01:34,961 --> 00:01:35,961
to start over.

30
00:01:36,863 --> 00:01:37,831
Do you really need to go this far

31
00:01:37,832 --> 00:01:39,165
just for Bai Xing?

32
00:01:39,966 --> 00:01:40,966
I already told you,

33
00:01:40,967 --> 00:01:42,569
I'm not trying to mess with him.

34
00:01:45,705 --> 00:01:47,774
No...

35
00:01:48,408 --> 00:01:49,342
I've wanted to say this

36
00:01:49,343 --> 00:01:50,877
since the moment I saw you again.

37
00:01:52,445 --> 00:01:55,047
But you just roll your eyes,

38
00:01:55,048 --> 00:01:56,149
snap at me,

39
00:01:56,583 --> 00:01:59,152
and won't even listen to me.

40
00:02:01,387 --> 00:02:02,989
Stop playing the victim.

41
00:02:04,557 --> 00:02:06,392
I'm way past the age

42
00:02:09,662 --> 00:02:11,029
of being blinded by love.

43
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:12,298
I don't fall for that anymore.

44
00:02:12,565 --> 00:02:13,833
Then what *do* you fall for?

45
00:02:29,449 --> 00:02:31,684
I'm not a kid anymore.

46
00:02:32,819 --> 00:02:33,819
Back then,

47
00:02:34,587 --> 00:02:35,655
you looked after me.

48
00:02:36,756 --> 00:02:38,525
Now, let me look after you.

49
00:02:39,993 --> 00:02:41,261
I've decided.

50
00:02:41,728 --> 00:02:42,862
Let's start over.

51
00:02:43,429 --> 00:02:44,664
I'm going to win you back.

52
00:02:49,169 --> 00:02:50,403
Start over?

53
00:02:51,738 --> 00:02:53,339
If it were really that easy,

54
00:02:55,608 --> 00:02:56,609
then

55
00:02:58,244 --> 00:02:58,745
why didn't you

56
00:02:58,746 --> 00:03:00,280
give me a chance to explain?
